<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/696014-many-of-the-reviews-below-mention-that">Many of the reviews below mention that Power fails to present &quot;the atrocities that the US supported/participated in&quot; — does anyone have a book recommendation that can provide this? I&#39;d like to read Power&#39;s book, but I&#39;d also like to have a balanced perspective on the US&#39;s role in genocide around the world.</a>
</div>
