<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41021476-embers-of-war"><img alt="Embers of War: The Fall of an Empire and the Making of America&#39;s Vietnam" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1533135451l/41021476._SX98_.jpg" />
