<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/29617055-fundamentals-of-genocide-and-mass-atrocity-prevention"><img alt="Fundamentals of Genocide and Mass Atrocity Prevention" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png" />
